panels.content:
* Use `Ctrl + o` combination for change tooltip view 
* Click on Row Name, for example `Original data (concentration)` for hide or show all panels incide.
* You can change date interval by right top button or select it on graph.
* You can enable/disable show data for metric by `Shift + click` on it name. Try it with `AQI: PM2.5, max` metric
* AQI detalization interval for `PM2.5` and `PM10` [specified in formula](https://www.airnow.gov/sites/default/files/2018-05/aqi-technical-assistance-document-may2016.pdf) - 1 day (`1d`). So it recommended, byt you can choose any interval
* Station location can be found at https://www.saveecobot.com/station/$device_id
